hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I live in London docsimon.com review But it is the connection with Hughes – the man who turned getting away from it all into an art form – that has really got the property world buzzing. At the time he bought the cabin, he was at the height of his powers, the richest man in the world and, as owner of RKO studios, one of the most powerful men in Hollywood. The list of actresses he dated reads like a who's who of the golden age of cinema: Bette Davis, Ava Gardner, Olivia de Havilland, Katherine Hepburn and Ginger Rogers.
